Cook Different | Frank Pinello⁠
⁠
If you know anything about the New York pizza scene, you’ll know Frank’s a big name. As the host of “The Pizza Show” on Vice and the owner of Best Pizza in Williamsburg, he’s become a household name among pizza aficionados. He’s traveled all over the world in search of the perfect slice, but he always comes back to his roots in Brooklyn.⁠
⁠
@bestpizza33⁠
⁠
This is how Frank is inspired to #CookDifferent. ⁠
⁠
#Gozney⁠

The love is #REAL.. Iv bought, borrowed, stole (😬), and have very kindly been gifted @hedleyandbennett gear for years.. When I met @ellenmariebennett 💥💯💥.. it all made sense!! @hedleyandbennett BEST IN THE GAME ✨💫✨ #EB your a real one 💙💪🏽 !! Made my day😘 Thank you 💛💚💙🧡❤️

@brianlpz120 one of the hardest working dependable and smart young men I know. There's no ceiling to your success. From LA TO BK many more memories ahead thank you and HAPPY BIRTHDAY u deserve it!💙🙌🏽🍕

I am so incredibly proud of the crew of #BESTPIZZA #800 #Grandst !! The newest addition to the #BP brand.. @fernandobelendez @dr_gigglez86 . I'm so lucky to have you guys in my life for so many years now! Great job 💯

Sitting home recovering from knee surgery reflecting on the first half of summer.. few weeks back I got to hang with @cooker.girl 💯💙! One of the realest , talented and hard working young cooks out there. Really glad we got to hang and talk pizza!  Enjoy the journey! Hope to see you soon 🙏🏽🇮🇹
Summer Highlights: Beautiful article, Block Island,Birthdays, Bum knee, PT, and me tickling the keys... 🍕🏝️🎂

Birthdays are a big deal @ #BESTPIZZA. This one is extra SPECIAL! @adrianlemus28 what a ride it's been... Thank you for so many years of hard work. After working a decade @ #Tabla for @dhmeyer and @floydcardoz (RIP🕊️) as they closed in 2010 We were just starting our journey. 14 years later here we are. The countless young men and women you mentored over the years, the intense attention to detail you work with everyday still inspires me! We all love you! I pray for another 20 years together 🤞🏽 🙏🏽🍕🙌🏽 .. Happy Birthday 🎈 and many many more my brother💙
